ion_y`, `width`, `height` (INTEGER)\n\n**Indexes:** tenant_id on events, users, dashboards; name on events; timestamp on events\n\n---\n\n### 3. **package.json Dependencies and Scripts**\n\n**Scripts:**\n- `build` - `tsc` (TypeScript compilation)\n- `lint` - `eslint src/` (Code quality check)\n- `test` - `vitest run` (Run tests)\n\n**devDependencies:**\n- TypeScript ^5.4.0\n- ESLint ^8.56.0 with @typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin and @typescript-eslint/parser (both ^7.0.0)\n- Vitest ^2.0.0 with @vitest/coverage-v8 ^2.0.0\n- Supertest ^7.0.0 (HTTP testing)\n- Type definitions for: Express, better-sqlite3, jsonwebtoken, supertest, uuid\n\n**dependencies:**\n- Express ^4.18.0\n- better-sqlite3 ^11.0.0\n- jsonwebtoken ^9.0.0\n- uuid ^10.0.0\n\n---\n\n### 4. **tsconfig.json Configuration**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"strict\": true,                    // Strict mode enabled\n    \"target\": \"ES2022\",\n    \"module\": \"Node16\",\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"Node16\",\n    \"outDir\": \"./dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"./src\",\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"declaration\": true               // Generate .d.ts files\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src/**/*\"],\n  \"exclude\": [\"node_modules\", \"dist\", \"tests\"]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. **ESLint Configuration (.eslintrc.cjs)**\n\n- Parser: @typescript-eslint/parser\n- Extends: plugin:@typescript-eslint/recommended\n- Custom rule: `@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars` with argsIgnorePattern `^_` and varsIgnorePattern `^_` (allows unused variables prefixed with underscore)\n- ECMAVersion: 2022\n- Source type: module\n\n---\n\n### 6. **vitest.config.ts Configuration**\n\n```typescript\n{\n  test: {\n    globals: true,        // Global test functions (describe, it, etc.)\n    testTimeout: 10000    // 10-second timeout per test\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Existing Source Files**\n\nThe **src/** directory is currently **empty** (only contains `.gitkeep`). All code needs to be written from scratch.\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Project Requirements Summary**\n\nThis is a **greenfield/complex TypeScript project** to build a **multi-tenant analytics dashboard API**:\n\n**5 Core Capabilities:**\n1. **User Management** - Register, login, JWT tokens, role-based access (admin/editor/viewer)\n2. **Data Ingestion** - Submit analytics events (single or batch)\n3. **Query Engine** - Count, timeseries, breakdown queries with tenant isolation\n4. **Dashboard Configuration** - Create/read/update/delete dashboards\n5. **Data Export** - CSV/JSON export with tenant isolation\n\n**Key Technical Requirements:**\n- Must export `createApp` function from `src/index.ts` or `src/app.ts` returning Express app\n- Use JWT for authentication with consistent token shape: `{sub, tid, iat, exp}`\n- Shared auth middleware and error handler returning `{error, code}` format\n- Proper tenant isolation in all query paths\n- Password hashing (not plaintext)\n- 401 status for unauthenticated protected routes\n- Must compile with strict TypeScript (ES2022, Node16)\n- Must pass ESLint checks\n\n---\n\nAll configuration is in place and ready for implementation. The project requires building the complete API from scratch in the `/workspace/src/` directory."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a109675 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 17080\ntool_uses: 12\nduration_ms: 21482</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cbdd94e3-af38-4ff5-af59-4a8bdc9e65f5","uuid":"0f8df339-fbc9-4f34-b816-fd0daed59695","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the entire project structure in /workspace. I need to understand:\n1. All files present (package.json, tsconfig.json, schema.sql, any existing src/ files)\n2. The database schema from schema.sql\n3. The package.json dependencies and scripts\n4. The tsconfig.json configuration\n5. Any ESLint configuration\n6. Any existing source files in src/\